latestPosts.caption:
Dance is the most pertinent way to control your emotions and feelings.  Now you are angry do a fine dance , your anger will run away,  the same can be repeated for others like cry, pain , frustration and so on . Dance being the most relevant way to supress , not actually suppress but to dominate your own feelings,  always helps us to be firm and determined towards our goals.You may be a dancer or may be not .Do dance.  Dance will not going to harm you , it will refresh you to come back from the dirty drain of our daily life .🌿……
